column2: SELECT dbo.fIAUFromEq(s.ra, s.dec), s.specobjId, s.ra, s.dec, p.z, p.zErr, s.class, j.g, plate, plate.mjd FROM Photoz p JOIN specobj s ON s.bestObjId = p.objId JOIN PhotoObj j ON j.ObjId = p.objId  JOIN platex AS plate ON other.plate = plate.plate AND other.mjd = plate.mjd  WHERE  (s.ra BETWEEN # AND # OR s.ra BETWEEN # AND #)  AND s.z <= #  AND photoErrorClass=#  AND p.zErr <= #  AND s.dec BETWEEN # and #  AND (class = &&&)  AND s.zWarning = #  ORDER BY p.z DESC
